dct_title_s: Ordnance survey of England and Wales : parts of sheets 4, 7 & 8
dct_description_sm: Map of Yorkshire. Relief shown by shading and spot heights. In upper margin: British Association 1906. "Revised in 1893-7 ... Reduced from the One Inch Map."--In margin below map. "Prepared especially for the British Association for the Advancement of Science. For distribution to Members."
